675B1D1F.Line3.121C9F: If it weren't for my master's armor, I wouldn't come back. The swamp can have the ruins. It was here first.

8ED7735D.Line1.121C9F: We should be cautious. Maugan's Folly was once a great Zakarum fortress, but since Caldeum stopped sending aid, it is now filled with deserters and thieves.
